23
00:01:16,768 --> 00:01:17,920
I worried they'd bully you.

24
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,519
See? I'm perfectly fine.

25
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:26,319
I know you like Cheng Ziru.

26
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,159
He's loyal to the Emperor.

27
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,959
He'll never side with us.

28
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,480
He might harm you.

29
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,000
Yu Feng,

30
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,280
t-take a look at my neck.

31
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,680
Does it need medicine?

32
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:37,040
If we don't treat it soon,

33
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,239
it'll scab over.

34
00:01:48,032 --> 00:01:52,000
=Episode 11=

35
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:57,879
Well?

36
00:01:58,208 --> 00:01:59,640
Did you take care of that boy?

37
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,280
Your Majesty,

38
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,319
