39
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,599
Please punish me.

40
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:10,960
Please rise.

41
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,039
Have you encountered difficulties?

42
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,319
Indeed.

43
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,800
Yu Feng is a great fighter.

44
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,879
It's reasonable you couldn't defeat him.

45
00:02:19,488 --> 00:02:20,039
Your Majesty,

46
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:23,719
