179
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,800
You fool.

180
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,919
(Is Xiao Hu)

181
00:08:39,519 --> 00:08:40,080
(my...)

182
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,039
You...

183
